14
00:01:30,547 --> 00:01:34,612
=Double Happiness=

15
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:38,008
=Episode 24=

16
00:02:18,142 --> 00:02:19,142
You go first.

17
00:02:19,501 --> 00:02:20,222
He's still asleep.

18
00:02:20,302 --> 00:02:20,942
We'll go up

19
00:02:21,022 --> 00:02:22,022
