00:40:56,982 --> 00:40:57,822
One day,

861
00:40:57,902 --> 00:40:58,823
I'll let them

862
00:40:58,903 --> 00:41:00,221
drive me crazy.

863
00:41:00,781 --> 00:41:02,221
The old one doesn't settle down.

864
00:41:02,502 --> 00:41:03,982
The young one doesn't care.

865
00:41:04,181 --> 00:41:07,382
The old one eats like a pig.
The young one insists on fasting.

866
00:41:08,181 --> 00:41:08,823
Why is life

867
00:41:08,903 --> 00:41:10,542
so tough for me?

868
00:41:11,342 --> 00:41:12,382
Youyou still isn't eating?

869
00:41:13,382 --> 00:41:14,382
No.

870
00:41:15,141 --> 00:41:16,781
She has refused to come out and eat.

871
00:41:17,502 --> 00:41:18,501
It's okay

872
00:41:18,581 --> 00:41:20,181
