873
00:41:20,261 --> 00:41:21,261
They won't starve.

874
00:41:24,542 --> 00:41:25,342
What are you doing?

875
00:41:25,502 --> 00:41:27,221
If she doesn't eat, then you don't.

876
00:41:27,942 --> 00:41:29,382
You're being unreasonable.

877
00:41:29,462 --> 00:41:31,141
You're being unreasonable daily.

878
00:41:31,221 --> 00:41:32,822
Why can't I be unreasonable once?

879
00:41:33,342 --> 00:41:34,342
Mom, Dad.

880
00:41:34,942 --> 00:41:35,942
I'll go check on her.

881
00:41:48,902 --> 00:41:49,902
Youyou.

882
00:41:51,542 --> 00:41:52,741
Is it okay if I come in?

883
00:42:03,982 --> 00:42:04,982
Sure.

884
00:42:07,502 --> 00:42:08,502
What's wrong?

885
00:42:09,902 --> 00:42:10,902
Chengyi.

886
00:42:21,862 --> 00:42:22,982
We were worried about you.

887
00:42:23,062 --> 00:42:24,221
Okay, it's fine.

888
00:42:24,822 --> 00:42:25,822
Chengyi.

889
00:42:27,621 --> 00:42:28,982
You can't betray me.

890
00:42:29,141 --> 00:42:30,501
I want to return to the cemetery.

891
00:42:30,581 --> 00:42:33,022
