I'm afraid they'll replace me.

892
00:42:35,062 --> 00:42:35,942
Alright.

893
00:42:36,062 --> 00:42:37,062
Chengyi.

894
00:42:37,741 --> 00:42:38,741
Chengyi.

895
00:42:38,822 --> 00:42:40,302
Don't look down on our cemetery.

896
00:42:40,382 --> 00:42:42,581
Yongshou Cemetery
is the best in Jiang City.

897
00:42:42,741 --> 00:42:44,221
Many college and graduate students

898
00:42:44,301 --> 00:42:45,822
are scrambling to work there.

899
00:42:46,301 --> 00:42:47,301
Really.

900
00:42:49,261 --> 00:42:50,261
I'm begging you.

901
00:42:58,462 --> 00:42:59,621
What does he mean?

902
00:43:03,261 --> 00:43:04,741
He'll settle it for me.

903
00:43:32,208 --> 00:43:38,663
♪A river connects
